-- Post Holdings to buy Michael Foods for $2.45 bln
-- By Siddharth Cavale in Bangalore
-- Thu Apr 17, 2014 06:09AM EDT
-- None



April 17 (Reuters) - Cereal maker Post Holdings Inc <POST.N> said it will buy Michael Foods Inc [MIKL.UL] for $2.45 billion to expand in the away-from-home breakfast business.

